{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2016}} [[File:Bochum Musikforum with tower.jpg|thumb|The music hall. Foyer in the former church of St. Mary.]] The '''Anneliese Brost Musikforum Ruhr''' is a [[music hall]] for classical music. It is located in [[Bochum]], Germany. It was opened on 28 October 2016. The building consists of three parts: an auditorium holding up to 1026 people, the entrance area in the middle (which is in the [[desacralized]] church of St. Marien), and a second hall which holds an audience of up to 250 people. The big hall is designed for [[symphony|symphonic]] concerts, the smaller one for [[chamber music]].
[[File:Bochum Musikforum interior west.jpg|thumb|Foyer at opening]] The hall is the home location of the ''[[Bochumer Symphoniker]]'' orchestra. The decision to build the Anneliese Brost Musikforum Ruhr was made with considerable backing from the American composer, [[Steven Sloane]]. <ref>[http://www.bochum.de/C12571A3001D56CE/vwContentByKey/W28ETEQN144BOLDDE/$FILE/Musikzentrum%20Konzeptpapier%20Endfassung_1.pdf Konzept Musikzentrum] (PDF; 560&nbsp;kB)</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Bochumer Musikhaus soll Generationen inspirieren|trans-title=| periodical=derwesten.de| publisher=WAZ| url=https://www.derwesten.de/staedte/bochum/bochumer-musikhaus-soll-generationen-inspirieren-id12314953.html| deadurl= |accessdate=2016-10-29| archiveurl=| archivedate=| last=Jürgen Boebers-Süßmann| date=28 October 2016| year=| month=| day=| language=German| pages=| quote=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Auch Herbert Grönemeyer schwärmt vom Musikforum|trans-title=| periodical=| publisher=Rurhnachrichten| url=https://www.ruhrnachrichten.de/leben-und-erleben/kultur-region/44787-Bochum~/Ausgekluegelte-Inszenierung-Das-erste-Konzert-im-Bochumer-Musikforum;art1541,3142117| deadurl=| format=| accessdate=2016-10-29|archiveurl=| archivedate=| last=Max Florian Kühlem| date=| year=| month=| day=| language=German| pages=| quote=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Kurzer Blick auf Leben und Wirken der Namensgeberin Anneliese Brost|trans-title=| periodical=| publisher=WAZ| url=https://www.derwesten.de/staedte/bochum/kurzer-blick-auf-leben-und-wirken-der-namensgeberin-anneliese-brost-aimp-id12315550.html| deadurl=| accessdate=2016-10-29| archiveurl=| archivedate=| last=Michael Weeke| date=29 October 2016| year=| month=| day=| language=German| pages=| quote=}}</ref>
