'''National Road 124''' is a national road of [[Cambodia]]. The road starts roughly {{convert|25|km}} east of [[Kampong Speu (town)|Kampong Speu]] off [[National Highway 1 (Cambodia)|National Highway 1]], following on from [[National Road 51 (Cambodia)|National Road 51]] in a southerly direction. At [[Khum Srang]] the road connects with [[National Road 125 (Cambodia)|National Road 125]] which leads directly north-west to Kampong Speu.
The road continues south passing through [[Prey Chek District]] before joining [[National Highway 3 (Cambodia)|National Highway 3]] several kilometres west of [[Dam Thnam]].
